<section id="learning-outcomes" class="slide level3">
<h3>Learning outcomes</h3>
<p>Upon completion of this course, you will be able to:</p>
<ul>
<li class="fragment">Understand the fundamentals of deep learning within the machine learning context</li>
<li class="fragment">Train a deep neural network, choosing the most appropriate characteristics depending on the type of problem, and optimizing the hyperparameters</li>
<li class="fragment">Describe the main architectures used in deep learning, as well as the most typical applications</li>
<li class="fragment">Identify the most appropriate deep learning algorithm for various types of problems in different domains.</li>
<li class="fragment">Implement deep learning algorithms using different tools.</li>
</ul>
</section>
